parameters:
Male Returnee Soldier: Coming to the Atomis Temple was a
good decision. It's truly a wonderful place that cleanses
the heart.

Male Returnee Soldier: Please listen, priest. I have taken
the lives of many people on the battlefield... I am a sinful
person.

Male Returnee Soldier: My heart feels lighter now. Please
make use of these few items as tools for your journey.

Male Veteran Soldier: I hope the Empire goes in the right
direction.

High Priest Laoco: I apologize for showing you such an
unsightly sight. I am High Priest Laoco of the Terios
religion.

High Priest Laoco: I will get straight to the point and tell
you all. I would like you to serve as escorts for the
priestesses of the Three Goddesses!

Priestess Sophia: Isn't that traditionally the job of the
Imperial Army?

High Priest Laoco: The Terios religion does not recognize
the legitimacy of Queen Caron. As a form of harassment, we
have decided to cancel the dispatch of escorts.
Thief Nora: How about asking General Atu!?

Clea: Yes, since we are familiar with each other, we might
be able to ask for their help.

High Priest Laoco: I have been told that I cannot act on my
own as someone in the position of a general.

High Priest Laoco: Various constraints have created the
current situation, so we need the power of the Adventurer's
Guild!
Clea: Understood, we will accept your request.

Mage Relm: Are you okay...? If something happens, it will
really become troublesome.

Mage Relm: There is no mistake because I, a mage from the
Magic Academy, am saying it.

Clea: Failure is not tolerated in the Adventurer's Guild,
regardless of the size of the request.
Clea: What seems to be the matter?

High Priest Laoco: No, I feel like I've seen you somewhere
before...

High Priest Laoco: Let's put that aside for now. The shrine
maidens will be arriving at the temple soon by carriage.
High Priest Laoco: Please let me know when you are ready.
High Priest Laoco: Are you ready?

High Priest Laoco: During the prayer ritual, the movement of
the shrine maidens is not allowed. If enemies appear, make
sure to defeat them before they reach the shrine maidens.

High Priest Laoco: I will begin preparations for the ritual.
Please take care of the shrine maidens.
High Priest Laoco: Thank you all so much!
High Priest Laoco: General Atu has also come to our aid...!

General Atu: While I was taking a walk, I happened to come
across some suspicious individuals! By chance, I joined
forces with the mighty adventurers from the Guild and
defeated them!

General Atu: No one should have any complaints, no matter
who they are! Hahaha, now that I have confirmed the safety
of the priestess, I shall return!
High Priest Laoco: Clea, regarding the name of your father--

High Priest Laoco: They say my daughter resembles her father
in appearance, especially her eyes... Ah, it brings back
memories.
Clea: C-Can you please tell me more about it!?

High Priest Laoco: First, please have an audience with the
priestesses. If you have any concerns, please let me know
after it's finished.

High Priest Laoco, First, please arrange a meeting with the
priestesses.
Clea: May I ask you about my father?
High Priest Laoco: He is the savior of my life.

High Priest Laoco: It happened several decades ago, but
there was a time when we were attacked by demon worshippers.

High Priest Laoco: At that time, he single-handedly wielded
a great sword and defeated the demon worshippers.

High Priest Laoco: But he protected me and suffered a
serious injury... I have truly done something terrible to
him.
Clea: I didn't know that such a thing had happened.

High Priest Laoco: After the late Lord Agnos passed away,
his achievements were highly praised, and he was bestowed
with vast farmland and a great sword, my lord.

High Priest Laoco: His daughter defeated a dragon and saved
the shrine maiden... I cannot help but feel the guidance of
the supreme god Sol.

Clea (The sword that belonged to my father... it was a gift
from the king, wasn't it?)

High Priest Laoco: Being an adventurer is a dangerous job.
Both I and the shrine maidens pray for your safety.

High Priest Laoco May the Supreme God Sol and the Three
Goddesses protect you all.

High Priest Laoco: So it seems you are all here... just as
he prophesied.
High Priest Laoco: General Atu was here until recently.
Clea: ...What was the general doing here?

High Priest Laoco: It states that as the general of the
empire, he fought to protect the royal family, and also
guaranteed the safety of the three goddesses' priestesses.

High Priest Laoco: I believe that the priestesses should
serve the king. This has been upheld since the founding of
the empire.

High Priest Laoco: Even if I were to lose my life, I will
fulfill my duty to prevent Queen Caron from destroying it.

The priestess of Actina: A priestess is someone who
sacrifices their name for their role, but as an individual,
I cannot tolerate Caron's tyranny!

Priestess of Actina: Dragon Slayer, please take this to
defeat Queen Caron.

Priestess of Imiserinos: The High Priest is our benefactor
who discovered us. Please ensure that his life is not taken
away.

Priestess of Imiserinos: May the blessings of Imiserinos be
with all of you, and may it become a source of strength for
you.

Priestess of Deire: To pick a fight with the empire... even
the goddess Deire would be surprised.

Priestess of Deire: Using this person, who is the empire's
poisonous woman, please defeat her for us.

Clea: I have no intention of fighting as a power struggle. I
am doing this for the sake of my friends and for the peace
of the empire.

Clea: And now I have more reasons to fight. I will
definitely defeat Queen Caron for the sake of everyone.

High Priest Laoco: Is the daughter of my savior trying to
save my life once again...

High Priest Laoco: May the glory of the main god Sol reach
everyone.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

High Priest Laoco May the Supreme God Sol and the Three
Goddesses protect you all.

parameters:
Royal Court Official Emoni: Ohoho, would you be willing to
recognize High Priestess Caron as the king's representative?

High Priestess Laoco: Since the founding of the empire, the
priests have served the king. We cannot serve anyone who is
not the king, no matter what!

High Priestess Laoco: Moreover, it is unacceptable to exile
the prince from the royal palace and abuse power by using
one's own son!

Royal Court Official Emoni: I understand the thoughts of the
High Priestess. I will make sure to convey them to Caron-
sama.

Royal Court Official Emoni: There are rumors that the demon
worshippers are targeting the priestesses.

Royal Court Official Emoni: If anything happens, it will
develop into a serious responsibility issue. I pray that the
ritual will be completed safely.
Royal Court Official Emoni: Good day, Dragon Slayer-sama.
Clea: If I remember correctly, it was at the royal palace...

Royal Court Official Emoni: You have a unique title in the
empire, there is no need for you to limit yourself to the
Adventurer's Guild!

Royal Court Official Emoni: If anything happens, please
contact me. I will relay the message to Queen Caron-sama!

Actina's Shrine Maiden: 'This time, the duty of being a
guardian was a noble cause.'

Actina's Shrine Maiden: 'I have heard that you are a warrior
who has slain dragons. You are truly blessed by the goddess
Actina!'

Actina's Shrine Maiden: Thank you very much for your help. I
am deeply moved by your heart that seeks to protect others.

Imiserinos Shrine Maiden: Just like the brave hero who saved
people from numerous demons... you are truly one who has
received the blessings of Imiserinos!

Dayley Shrine Maiden: Thank you for taking down those damn
bastards for me. I'm grateful.

Dayley Shrine Maiden: I was thrilled by your skill and heart
that can slay both humans and dragons. You truly feel like
one who has received the blessings of Dayley!
Mage Relm: It feels much more vulgar than I expected...

Priestess Sophia: There has been a dispute over which of the
three goddesses is the eldest... That myth has been passed
down, for better or for worse.

Priestess Sophia: Because you're at such a young age, you
know~
Thief Nora: Fighting is no good, you know~!

Actina's Shrine Maiden: Ohhon! I am grateful that the ritual
has been successfully completed.

Actina's Shrine Maiden: Currently, when there is a divine
oracle and the palace has become an untrustworthy entity, we
will rely on you for the request.

Actina's Shrine Maiden: I want you to accept this as a
reward for being a Dragon Slayer and for your escort this
time.
Dayley Shrine Maiden: Why are you the one in charge?

Imiserinos Shrine Maiden: Isn't it my job to express
gratitude to the Dragon Slayer?
Thief Nora: That's why fighting is no good, you know~!
Clea (I need to go ask Mr. Laocoön about my father.)

parameters:
The priestess of Actina believes that the eldest daughter of
the goddess is the goddess Actina, and the dragon slayer
shares the same belief.
Maiden of Actina: 'I'm glad you've come, Dragon Slayer!'

Maiden of Actina: 'Now, the Empire is once again facing the
threat of the immortal demon Amedol, who is worshipped by
the demon bride Ancos!'

Mage Relm: T-This is strange! Ancos should have been
defeated by the Magic Academy!

Priestess Sophia: This is strange. Ancos should have been
defeated by the Terios Church, right?

Maiden of Actina: That was just a facade. Even with all the
factions united, they couldn't completely kill him.

Maiden of Actina: The Empire, in an attempt to prolong his
life, sealed him away and attempted to subdue him by
erecting multiple barriers to contain him.
Clea: Will our job be to reinforce the barriers?
Maiden of Actina: That won't be a fundamental solution.

Maiden of Actina: The request will be to deliberately undo
the barriers and completely kill Ancos.

Thief Nora: Ah, isn't it dangerous...? You don't have to do
something so risky, you know.

Maiden of Actina: It's only a matter of time. The demon
worshippers are desperate for the revival of Ancos.

Maiden of Actina: If we can kill him in his current state
before he fully revives, it should be possible...!

Maiden of Actina: If we succeed in subduing Ancos, not only
will we receive honor, but we will also be given a special
reward.

Clea: If it's a crisis for the Empire, we will definitely
defeat Ancos.

Maiden of Actina: This is the key to undo the barriers. I
believe in you.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Actina's Priestess: She is a witch who worships the demon
lord Amedol. As the eldest daughter of the high priestess, I
absolutely cannot forgive her.

Oh, Dragon Slayer! I heard there has been a change in
magical energy near the village of Lypi.
Could it be that you have defeated Ancos!?

Clea: I have shattered what seemed to be a soul. I believe
it will never revive again.

Actina's Priestess: It was the right decision to count on
you! I don't like it, but let's rely on the priestess of
Imiserinos for the sealing.

Actina's Priestess: You protected us during the ritual and
defeated the threat of the dragon and the empire known as
Ancos.

Actina's Priestess: As a priestess serving the goddess
Actina, I will guide you to a place connected to the hero.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Actina's Priestess: The fact that I have encountered a hero
like you is something that the previous generations of
Actina's priestesses would surely be jealous of.

Actina's Priestess: Do you think we stand a chance against
the seasoned Goblin Slayer and Dragon Slayer?

Actina's Priestess: I'm glad you've returned! I believed
that as a Dragon Slayer, you would accomplish it.

Clea: We had a battle with the statue of the goddess Actina
at the deepest part, and there I obtained a strange cloth.
Do you happen to know anything about it?

Actina's Priestess: It looks like silk... but strangely, I
don't feel any weight at all.

Actina's Priestess: From what I've heard, it was originally
prepared for the Hero-sama.

Actina's Priestess: If you think about it that way, there's
no mistake that it's something to be used in battle.

Actina's Priestess: Hey, why don't you perform a victory
ritual?

Sophia the Priestess: There is a ritual where a prestigious
individual is adorned with a cloth around their neck as a
symbol of their achievements.

Actina's Priestess: I apologize for not knowing how to use
this cloth, but please understand that the victory ritual is
the greatest praise.

Clea: Thank you very much. On behalf of my comrades, I will
accept it.

Mage Relm: Please throw away the cloth somewhere! An unknown
power is starting to envelop Clea-san--
Clea: --Ah, I lost consciousness for a moment.

Clea: I don't think I'm injured... I don't feel any pain, so
I should be fine.

Priestess Sophia: Clea-chan's attire... it's as if she has
transformed into the appearance of the goddess Actina.
Mage Relm: Ah, um, is your hair growing...?
Thief Nora: Long hair suits you sooo well!

Clea: I don't quite understand, but... are you saying that
the cloth from earlier transformed into this attire?
Clea: What should I do with this?

Priestess of Actina: Of course, it belongs to the Dragon
Slayer.

Priestess of Actina: I want you to use it as the attire of
the goddess Actina.

Priestess of Imiserinos: The one who guided the hero was the
goddess Imiserinos. Wouldn't it be appropriate to wear the
attire of the goddess Imiserinos here?

Priestess of Deirei: Hey hey, it was me who proposed the
victory ritual. Isn't it the usual flow to wear the attire
of the goddess Deirei here?
Thief Nora: That's why~ fighting is no good, you know!

Priestess of Actina: Oh my, regardless of the name, I am
convinced that all three goddesses want you to use it.
実績 女神アクティナの装束

Priestess of Actina: 'If you ever feel like testing your
skills and delivering a message from the hero, please come
to the 'Sunken City'.'
実績 勇者への挑戦

Priestess of Actina: This time, all the priestesses who have
had various experiences are praying for the victory of the
Dragon Slayer.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

The priestess of Actina believes that the eldest daughter of
the goddess is the goddess Actina, and the dragon slayer
shares the same belief.

Imiserinos Shrine Maiden: I pray for the safety of
everyone's journey. May the blessings of the goddess
Imiserinos be with you all.

Priestess of Imiserinos: 'Thank you all for coming. I would
like you to carry out the divine revelation I have

Priestess of Imiserinos: I can hear the voices of those who

Priestess of Imiserinos: Receiving divine revelations is the

priests.

Priestess of Imiserinos: Hero Clea, Priestess Sophia, please

Priestess Sophia: I believe it is something that is beyond
someone like me, a priestess...

Priestess of Imiserinos: A priestess is someone who becomes
[through salvation]. Please consider this opportunity as a
place for your growth.

Priestess Sophia: ...Understood. Although I myself am a lost
soul, I will carry out the divine revelation.

Clea: I am honored to be able to accept the request from the
Priestess-sama without any problems.

Priestess of Imiserinos: There are three lost souls...
Please resolve each of their doubts and carry out their
salvation.

Priestess of Imiserinos: 'May the lost souls be blessed with
the divine protection of the goddess Imiserinos.'
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

\CL Area Liberation\c[18]\CL Valley Region / Sphiri
Mines\c[0]

Priestess of Imiserinos, please take care of the lost souls

Is the powerful voice seeking salvation from the Valkyrie
Guild's Goat... his?

Please make sure to rescue him, the priestess of Imiserinos.
What he needs is not a battle, but healing.

Actina's Priestess: That's not true! You're not the only one

Clea: What do you mean by that?

Actina's Priestess: The goat of the Valkyrie Guild seeks an

monster!

Actina's Priestess: In order to answer that voice... we have
dispatched the greatest warrior as a messenger of Actina's

Actina's Priestess: You all know him too.

Actina's Priestess: As seasoned warriors who have continued
to hunt monsters, you should understand the strength of

Imiserinos' priestess: I won't allow that...! They will

Priestess Sophia: Yes, I will definitely rescue him.

Clea (Which will be resolved first... the curse or defeating

3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Actina's Priestess: Do you think we stand a chance against
the seasoned Goblin Slayer and Dragon Slayer?

Imiserinos' priestess: 'Goat is suffering greatly. The sword

Imiserinos' priestess: It is the warm hand of Imiserinos.

Clea: What should we do? We don't have any clues to save

Imiserinos' priestess: If someone possesses the hand of

Mage Relm: The hand of salvation... in other words, a

Priestess Sophia: N-No, it's impossible! We can't entrust

Mage Relm: If you're aware of it, then please stop...

Imiserinos' priestess: I should have mentioned before that a

Imiserinos' priestess: If you're feeling uneasy, rely on

Priestess Sophia: I don't have confidence as a priestess,

Thief Nora: But if we don't hurry, Goat-san will be taken by

Priestess Sophia: I don't have the qualifications to be a

Mage Relm: Shall we go to the Magic Academy? There might be

Clea: ...I understand, let's go to the academy.

Imiserinos' Shrine Maiden: Hurry... the voices are getting

Imiserinos' Shrine Maiden: Yes, they have accomplished it. I

Imiserinos' Shrine Maiden: I have won.

Imiserinos' Shrine Maiden: Did you hear? They won the battle

Imiserinos' Shrine Maiden: I have shown you an unsightly

Dayley's Shrine Maiden: I saw the figure of a girl who
